episodes.title: The Trans Vegan Death Cult (Zizians)
episodes.description:
Trans vegan death cult. It’s potentially an interesting discussion. Is there a link between something like veganism and cultism? A lot of conservatives would say “yea," and of course, they are the ones highlighting the “trans vegan” aspect of this cult. But I think even reasonable people who aren’t anti-vegan because “bacon good” are curious.
